@@TJvScrollBar.CMCtl3DChanged
Summary
  Responds when the Ctrl3D property changes.
Description
  CMCtl3DChanged is called automatically when the Ctl3D property changes. It triggers the 
  OnCtl3DChanged event.
Parameters
  Msg - Represents the parameters of the Windows message that informs the scroll bar of the Ctl3D 
        change.
See Also
  OnCtl3DChanged
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvScrollBar.CMMouseEnter
Summary
  Responds when the mouse pointer moves over the scroll bar.
Description
  CMMouseEnter is called automatically when the mouse pointer moves over the scroll bar. It sets the
  hint color for the application to the property specified by HintColor, sets the Ctl3D property
  to true if property HotTrack is true, and triggers the OnMouseEnter event.
Parameters
  Msg - Represents the parameters of the Windows message that informs the scroll bar of the event.
See Also
  CMMouseLeave, OnMouseEnter, OnMouseLeave
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvScrollBar.CMMouseLeave
Summary
  Responds when the mouse pointer moves off the scroll bar.
Description
  CMMouseEnter is called automatically when the mouse pointer moves off the scroll bar. It resets the
  hint color for the application, sets the Ctl3D property to false if property HotTrack is true, and
  triggers the OnMouseLeave event.
Parameters
  Msg - Represents the parameters of the Windows message that informs the scroll bar of the event.
See Also
  CMMouseEnter, OnMouseEnter, OnMouseLeave
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvScrollBar.CMParentColorChanged
Summary
  Responds when the color of the parent of the scroll bar changes.
Description
  CMParentColorChanged is called automatically when the color of the parent of the scroll bar changes.
  It triggers the OnParentColorChange event.
Parameters
  Msg - Represents the parameters of the Windows message that informs the scroll bar of the parent
        color change.
See Also
  OnParentColorChange
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvScrollBar.HintColor
Summary
  Determines the color of the hint boxes for the Help Hints for the scroll bar.
Description
  Use HintColor to specify the hint box color. A default color value of clInfoBk is set for the
  HintColor property in the constructor when the application is created. To change the HintColor
  assign it a new TColor value.
See Also
  HotTrack
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvScrollBar.HotTrack
Summary
  Specifies whether the scroll bar is highlighted when the mouse passes over it.
Description
  Set HotTrack to True to provide visual feedback when the mouse passes over the scroll bar. When 
  HotTrack is False, there is no visual feedback when the mouse passes over the scroll bar.
See Also 
  OnMouseEnter, OnMouseLeave
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvScrollBar.OnCtl3DChanged
Summary
  Occurs when the Ctl3D property of the scroll bar changes.
Description
  Write an OnCtl3DChanged event handler to take specific action when the Ctl3D property changes.
See Also
  OnParentColorChange
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvScrollBar.OnMouseEnter
Summary
  Occurs when the mouse pointer moves over the scroll bar.
Description
  Write an OnMouseEnter event handler to take specific action when the user moves the mouse over the
  scroll bar.
See Also
  HotTrack, OnMouseLeave 
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvScrollBar.OnMouseLeave
Summary
  Occurs when the mouse pointer moves off the scroll bar.
Description
  Write an OnMouseLeave event handler to take specific action when the user moves the mouse off the
  scroll bar.
See Also
  HotTrack, OnMouseEnter
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvScrollBar.OnParentColorChange
Summary
  Occurs when the color property for the parent of the scroll bar changes.
Description
  Write an OnParentColorChange event to take specific action when the ParentColor property changes.
See Also
  OnCtl3DChanged
